test_list_of_zeros:
assert [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, ...] == []
  Left contains 7 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]
test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [93, 93, 93, 93, 93, 93, ...] == []
  Left contains 7 more items, first extra item: 93
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [93, 93, 93, 93, 93, 93, 93]
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [930, 930, 93...930, 930, ...] == []
  Left contains 7 more items, first extra item: 930
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [930, 930, 930, 930, 930, 930, 930]
